@kingofny:
Thanks for the encouragement but I can hardly be compared to 3x0 who had already achieved trusted uploader status when he was uploading recent torrents before HR. Case in point the lack of seeds I have for my upload of The Next Three Days which HR has also uploaded. So I'll stick to uploading older movies I think.

@RAYMONDryche:
I never questioned how you got your VIP status. I have the utmost respect for all trusted and VIP uploaders for their contribution to the community. Without 3x0 Handbrake instructions I'd still be waiting in vain for HR and others to upload my movie requests rather than be uploading handheld movies myself.
